              <h4 class="dropbox__title">
                What is Bakalavr.az and how does it work?
              </h4>
              <div class="dropbox__icon">
                <img src="./images/images/icon-chevron-down.svg" alt="icon" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropbox__description">
              <p>
                Bakalavr.az is a comprehensive virtual meeting platform designed
                for students and tutors. It offers advanced real-time
                communication, customizable meeting rooms, and secure closed
