              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dropbox">
            <div class="dropbox__closed">
              <h4 class="dropbox__title">
                How does the homework system in Bakalavr.az work?
              </h4>
              <div class="dropbox__icon">
                <img src="./images/images/icon-chevron-down.svg" alt="icon" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropbox__description">
              <p>
                The homework system in Bakalavr.az allows tutors to assign,
                track, and grade homework efficiently. Students can submit their
                homework directly through the platform, and tutors can provide
                feedback and grades in real-time. This system ensures that
                students stay on top of their assignments and receive timely
                support from their tutors.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dropbox">
            <div class="dropbox__closed">
              <h4 class="dropbox__title">How does Live Chat work?</h4>
              <div class="dropbox__icon">
                <img src="./images/images/icon-chevron-down.svg" alt="icon" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropbox__description">
              <p>
                The live chat feature on Bakalavr.az provides real-time support
                for users. Admins are available to assist with any questions or
                issues that may arise during the use of the platform. Whether
                you need help navigating the site, troubleshooting technical
                problems, or understanding how to use specific features, our
                live chat ensures that you get immediate assistance. This
                feature enhances the user experience by offering prompt and
                personalized support, ensuring that your virtual learning and
                meeting sessions run smoothly.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="dropbox">
            <div class="dropbox__closed">
              <h4 class="dropbox__title">
                How does the chat feature on Bakalavr.az ensure user privacy?
              </h4>
              <div class="dropbox__icon">
                <img src="./images/images/icon-chevron-down.svg" alt="icon" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="dropbox__description">
              <p>
                The chat feature on Bakalavr.az facilitates seamless real-time
                communication between students and tutors, enhancing the virtual
                learning experience. To ensure user privacy, we do not store
                chat messages in our database. This means that all
                communications are temporary and are not saved once the session
                ends. Our commitment to protecting your privacy ensures that
                your conversations remain confidential and secure, providing you
                with peace of mind while using our platform.
              </p>
